        Description copied from interface: OWLDataFactory

        getOWLClass in interface OWLDataFactory

        iri - The abbreviated IRI, which is of the form PREFIX_NAME:RC, where PREFIX_NAME may be the empty string (the default prefix). Cannot be null. Note that abbreviated IRIs always contain a colon as a delimiter, even if the prefix name is the empty string.
